title: Nexus Omnibus (v01 - v04) (- Nem -)
description: First the headaches, then the nightmares of mass murderers who must die - by his hand, the hand that wields the energy of a living sun, the hand of Nexus! Possessing limitless power, Nexus is the greatest avenger in history, but his power and purpose come from an alien race with their own agenda. Is Nexus a hero or pawn? Deliverer or destroyer? God or devil? Created by Mike Baron and Steve Rude, Nexus is a science-fiction superhero masterpiece, and Nexus Omnibus Volume 1 features over 400 story pages of the award-winning series.
